  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together whiskey, soy sauce, honey, ginger, and garlic.",
    "Add the fish chunks to the marinade and mix well. Cover and refrigerate for at least 30 minutes.",
    "Thread the marinated fish onto skewers, leaving a small space between each piece.",
    "Brush the skewers with vegetable oil and season with salt and pepper.",
    "Grill the skewers for 8-10 minutes, or until the fish is cooked through and flakes easily with a fork.",
